.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-ingredients-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-ingredients-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-ingredients-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-ingredients-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-ingredients-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-ingredients-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-ingredients-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-ingredients.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-home-espresso-makers\"\u003eHome Espresso Makers\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe’ve tried many espresso makers over the years, and here are our favorites at different price points and skill levels:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3NF57oC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eCafe Automatic Espresso Machine\u003c/a\u003e – My current machine. It uses any whole beans, so if you use high quality beans you’ll get high quality espresso. It makes espresso shots automatically (no barista skills required) and includes a milk frothing wand to heat and froth milk. We’ve used this machine almost every day since we got it nine months ago and we love it! It comes in three colors.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/41UPTAv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eStovetop Espresso\u003c/a\u003e – This is the cheapest way to make espresso at home. It’s more labor intensive and you will also need a way to grind your beans for best results. But, this is a classic method that works great when done well.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3p4SiK4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eBreville Barista Touch \u003c/a\u003e– We bought this for a good friend as a wedding gift once and they said they love it. It’s a higher end machine that you will need some barista skills to operate, but it’s an excellent home espresso maker.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/44oKtPw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eNespresso Vertuo\u003c/a\u003e – For those who want an espresso maker that uses pods, this is my favorite. Depending what pod you use, it can make espresso or coffee.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/caramel-macchiato/?tp_image_id=118589\" data-pin-title=\"caramel macchiato\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-recipe.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-recipe.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-recipe-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-recipe-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-recipe-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-recipe-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-recipe-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-recipe-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/caramel-macchiato-recipe-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/c